        <item>
            <title>Version 2.0.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Rewrote OpenGL render pipeline — steady 24fps on 4K HEVC Dolby Vision</li>
                    <li>Dual-mode seeking: instant keyframe for slider, frame-accurate for keyboard</li>
                    <li>Seek times reduced from 4+ seconds to under 50ms on 4K HEVC</li>
                    <li>Audio stats filter only active in music mode</li>
                    <li>Disabled MKV subtitle preroll by default</li>
                    <li>Loading spinner delayed 1s to eliminate flash</li>
